      "writtenOn": "2018-11-09T16:45:23Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Precompiled code has to live in a different location. We use the following steps:\n\n1) Check in the source code as an archive in prebuilts/android-emulator-build/archive and update PACKAGES.TXT\n2) Create a build script that can compile the checked in archive. Our compile scripts live in ./android/scripts. See ./android/scripts/build-libusb.sh for example.\n3) Create an ./android/build/cmake/config/emu-PACKAGE-config.cmake which defines the precompiled target so we can use it.",
      "revId": "642358fa323f0c22ad104701c0c7df14fee983e3",
      "serverId": "85c56323-6fa9-3386-8a01-6480fb634889",
